===Noun===
'''veterinarian'''
{{wikipedia}}
# A [[medical]] [[doctor]] who [[treat]]s non-human [[animal]]s.  In the USA, has the degree "[[DVM]]" or "[[VMD]]", and is addressed as "[[Dr.]]".  In Great Britain and other countries, has the degree "[[BVSc]]".

